HEADWORD: intermediate school
<hw>in`ter*me"di*ate school`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A
school having grades at a level between the lower primary grades and the
upper secondary grades, being variously grades 4 through 6, or grades 7
through 9, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
